+# Phase 0287-r5-r2-r1 — ProjectV2 view endpoint context fix
+
+The previous endpoint patch used a hand-written hunk whose context did not match
+the real 446-line script. This corrective patch is generated from the exact
+current function block.
+
+Live probes proved that the user login must be used for the view endpoint:
+
+```text
+users/58338908/projectsV2/3/views → 404
+users/newicody/projectsV2/3/views → validation reached
+```
+
+The reconciler now uses `plan.owner`; `user_id` remains report metadata only.
+The remaining guide compatibility markers are restored and the r5-r1 rule is
+made cumulative.
