+# ProjectV2 view endpoint context fix
+
+```python
+fields_endpoint = (
+    f"users/{plan.owner}/projectsV2/{plan.number}/fields"
+)
+views_endpoint = (
+    f"users/{plan.owner}/projectsV2/{plan.number}/views"
+)
+```
+
+Both user-owned REST surfaces now consistently use the configured owner login.
+The numeric id remains visible in the preview report for diagnostics.
+
+After applying this patch, copy the reconciler into `newicody/projects`, run a
+new preview, confirm the new digest, and create the remaining views.
